        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "In this notation, we have sn = 2015 (mod 10000) if and only if n = 3m + 1 for some nonnegative integer m for which m = 400 (mod 1000) and f (m) = −1. Since 400 = 112211(3), the first such term in the sequence is in fact s1201 = 12015.",
